function bind(player,args){
    try {
    handlerClass = java.lang.Class.forName("org.hyperion.rs2.packet."+args[2]);
    org.hyperion.rs2.net.PacketManager.getPacketManager().bind(java.lang.Integer.parseInt(args[1]), handlerClass.newInstance());
	player.getActionSender.sendMessage("Bound packet: "+args[1]+" to "+args[2]);
} catch (e if e.javaException instanceof java.lang.ClassNotFoundException) {
        player.getActionSender().sendMessage("Class not found "+"org.hyperion.rs2.packet."+args[2]);
    }
}
